                <listApp><app><note>Text after Manganaro 1994</note></app></listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#FP">
                <p>Farewell worthy Studiosos! He lived for 60 years after being a pastoral cantor.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="#FP">
                <p>Addio, degno Studiosos. Egli visse 60 anni essendo stato un cantore bucolico.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p><!--commented out pending revision-->
                    <!--'Studiose chreste chaire', age in years, and defined as a ludiastes. I.e. epitaph of Studiosus. Died age 60, not age 7 as some earlier eds. sugg'd. Article by Valentini is on such performers / actors more generally. Manganaro 1963 says lost.--></p>
            </div>
